<chapter>
<title>Gentoo's Licensing Choice</title>
<section>
<title>The Creative Commons / Attribution - Share Alike License</title>
<body>

<p>
Gentoo has chosen to use the <uri
link="http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/1.0">CC-BY-SA</uri>
license for its documentation. This license provides us everything we
need for our documentation.
</p>

<p>
With CC-BY-SA, the documentation must have its sourcecode available to
the world. It can be copied, distributed and modified freely. However,
every change to the documentation may not result in the loss of other
authors/editors their credentials. Every change must also be publicised
freely under the CC-BY-SA license.
</p>

</body>
</section>
</chapter>
